accessrestrict.head: Access
accessrestrict.p: The collection is open to researchers without restrictions.

userestrict.head: Use Restrictions
userestrict.p: Questions about literary property rights should be directed to the Head of Special Collections.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: [Identification of item], Old Dominion University Photograph Collection, [Box number], [Folder number], Special Collections, Perry Library, Old Dominion University, Norfolk, Virginia.

acqinfo.head: Acquisition Information
acqinfo.p: Transferred to Special Collections from the University Relations office and University Photographer.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Content Information
scopecontent.p: This collection includes a variety of photographs covering the history of the University from 1930 to the 1990s. Photographic subjects include, students, faculty, administrators, academic departments, buildings and grounds, events, sororities, fraternities, sports, convocations, musical and theatrical performances, guest speakers, and student organizations.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The collection is organized into series chronologically by decade. Within each series the photographs are organized alphabetically by subject.

arrangement.head: Organization
arrangement.p: The collection is divided into the following series: Series I: 1930s (Box 1); Series II: 1940s (Boxes 2-3); Series III: 1950s (Boxes 4-26); Series IV: 1960s (Boxes 27-54); Series V: 1970s (Boxes 55-78); Series VI: Negatives (Boxes 79-83); Series VII: Slides Relating to ODU History (Box 84); Series VIII: Transparencies and Postcards (Box 85); Series IX: 1980s (Boxes 86-97); Series X: 1990s (Boxes 98-120).
